snippet.title: Squeen's Adventure: Alien Edition | Official Trailer 2021
snippet.description:
Squeen's spaceship has crash-landed onto earth, now that wouldn't be so bad, but his phone is dying and he needs to get to a charger quick! Help our alien pal in getting a brand new ship and getting back to his home planet.

This is a full remaster to the original Squeen's Adventure. Thanks to ArcadeGamer for producing the remakes of the level music.

GameJolt Link: https://gamejolt.com/games/squeenae/665456
Itch Link: https://jupitr-entertainment.itch.io/sa-ae
